* The temporary solution for the Myfunction_1.java:
**<Solution 1>**.  Multiply each coefficient of the formula by 2 (e.g. 2*a + 4*b + 6*c = 44)
After a lot of tests, I found that if the coefficients of the formula are not equal to 1, then the result will be right. 
The output will be:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/41780406/43523218-455c1d52-95ce-11e8-9101-c2c8d8f38d9c.png)

